mispronounce.definition: To pronounce (a word, phrase, etc.) incorrectly.

pounder.definition: A vessel in which something is pounded, or an implement used in pounding.

beeswax.definition: A wax secreted by bees from which they make honeycomb; or, the processed form of this wax used in the manufacture of various goods.
